How to use(you should install Herwig first):
  1. Clone these file
    $ git clone ...
    
  2. Activate the herwig 
    $ source /path to Herwig/bin/activate ##Note it MUST be ABSOLUTE path
    $ export PATH=/path to Herwig/bin:$PATH
  3.go to this file you clone
    $ cd /.../QCD-event-Pythia-Herwig-Sherpa/Herwig
    
  4. Change the LHC.in line 173: "set /Herwig/Analysis/HepMCFile:Filename /home/ja2006203966/event/HerwigLHC.hepmc" 
  to the hepmc2 output path you want.
  
  5. Read LHC.in
    $ Herwig read LHC.in
    
  6. Run LHC.run
    $ Herwig run LHC.run -N 100(number of event you want)
